Static Bearer attach header plumbing.

Adds generic client-side Bearer header support for opencode attach:

  - OPENCODE_SERVER_BEARER env in core flags.
  - ServerAuth.header() prefers credentials.bearer / OPENCODE_SERVER_BEARER over Basic auth.
  - opencode attach --bearer passes a Bearer token into SDK request headers.

Server-side opencode does NOT validate the Bearer. This patch only lets clients send it, for deployments where a reverse proxy validates JWTs before forwarding to opencode.

